{West Dreyton farm:I.Leonard}is the farmer.Names of fields:- Brake, Track field, Roundabout, 6 Acres, Past 6 Acres, Longfield, Woodlands, Quarry field, Hunting Gate, Bottom field and Front field.
When you look at the bottom gate of the Front field Track field is on your left next to it is Quarry field. They slope down to your right and Front field slopes down to your left.He keeps a herd of{cows}and six{bantams.}
In the winter he looks after some other peoples sheep. There is a{slurry {pit,}a{silage shed,}two{cubicles}one indoors and one outdoors, a{hay barn} and a place where he keeps some{straw. There is a{sheepdog}called Pip who is still a puppy.The farm covers about {66 acres. }
